/-- An equivalence between `SymmetryType` and permutation of edges, vertices and half-edges
satisfying `Hom.Cond`. -/
def FeynmanDiagram.symmetryTypeEquiv {P : PreFeynmanRule} (F : FeynmanDiagram P) : FeynmanDiagram.SymmetryType F ≃ { S // FeynmanDiagram.Hom.Cond ⇑S.1 ⇑S.2.1 ⇑S.2.2 }

