/-- The symmetry factor can be defined as the cardinal of the symmetry type.
In general this is not a finite number. -/
def FeynmanDiagram.cardSymmetryFactor {P : PreFeynmanRule} (F : FeynmanDiagram P) : Cardinal.{0}

